Baselines \& Methods.
We aim to augment LLMs with temporally relevant information for answering entity-centric questions and compare various augmentation strategies. Unlike existing RAG methods, which retrieve passages from large generic data indices, we employ strong baselines that retrieve from an entity-centric datastore (detailed in Section (ref)). We evaluate the following methods within the RAG framework to address our temporal QA task: